<plot>One of a series of shorts produced by Fox Movietone News, in which Vyvyan Donner, the fashion-segment director/producer of the newsreels, gets to spread her wings on a short dedicated just to fashion. The subject matter in this entry is play-clothes for indoors and outdoors, in the north and south of the United States, and in winter or summer. Ilka Chase provides her usual witty commentary, written by Vyvyan Donner. The 1940 male also got tips on what to wear at the beach or dancing under a tropical moon.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?190140</url></doc>
